member.remarks:
            When passing custom data, it's recommended to use  to build it.


            Also, it is recommended to initialize the value within the passed function to reduce performance when the used log level is disabled:
            
            var customData = () => new CustomDataCollection().Add("key1", "value1").Add("key2", false);
            _logger.LogTrace(eventId, customData, "Message");
            
            
            Instead of:
            
            var customData = new CustomDataCollection().Add("key1", "value,1").Add("key2", false);
            _logger.LogTrace(eventId, () => customData, "Message");

